This study focused on SDG 7 and SDG 13, and their subgoals. It combined the synergistic effect between carbon emission reduction and environmental pollution reduction (Chen et al., 2023; Jiang et al., 2023), constructed an evaluation system of the CERC, and explained the basis for the construction of the indicator system and its role in the CERC (Table 1
